values: Yesturday had my firts day of training. It was awesome I didnt really do anyhing i sat in the "sacs" for most of the night.  the only neg of the job is fluffing the sacs gets supre annoyinh and your finger tips get really sore cuz it rubs against them every time. Anyways, Today was a good day - minus the fact i almost fell asleep in every class. oh well ill catch up on sleep this weekend.  THis weekend is gonna rock. Going to purdue wiht laura staying wiht her friend. its his birthday=partys!!! Nuthing elses to report. Peace, love, and happiness. I need more of all three of those - i actually think we could all use some more. SO I LOVE ALL OF YOU! I WANT YOU ALL TO BE HAPPY AND BE AT PEACE!

Im sick of school. as most of you know i dont really go to school alot. and i havent missed in over a month and a half so im due for a mental heath day.  but i really dont like it i have soo much homewokr all the sudden and senroitis is really kicking in. YUCK! but the good news i got a job finally! i am no longer unemployed. I am the newest employee of the love sac. HAHA  HELL YEA! it is a joke. i worked at a day care and got paid less to take care of other peoples kids. something is wrong wiht our society.  anyways back to homewokr. mwah leave love

Another weekend is over and stuff is changing - time is moving too fast and im scared.  So much stuff is going on in my head but of course i cant post it or else i will have a trillion (exageration) people either asking me whats wrong, being pissed at me, or just thinking that im going pyscho and i dont feel like dealign wiht that right now.  Its weird people say that senior year you realize all things about your friends, family, and most impportantly yourself. This is sooo true.  In the past month or so i have learned so much about myself. Ive been doing alot of thinking, cuz of course i cant pay attention in class so i have some tiem to think, And from this moment on i am going to make an active effort to change some aspects of my life. This sounds messed but someone told me that they made a list of the characteristics theyt liked abotu themself and the ones they didnt like. this way they could keep the possitives and change the negs. Maybe seeing it in writting and having a goal will help me get motivated.  Needless to say, it should be interesting to see how this will all work out.  
Im going to leave you with this thought that you will hopefully apply to your daily life. TREAT OTHERS AS YOU WOULD LIKE TO BE TREATED!!!!!! im so sick of this shit...

This is messed up.  I swear i am bipolar. I can be super happy one minute and the next pissed at the world. there is noway this is normal.  I think im just really stressed right now and overwhelmed basically by life.  i need some thinking time. on that note I visited purdue and indiana this weekend.  Imleaning towards purdue but i still need to ehar from U of I and visit Iwoa. indiana was too spread out for me even though they had the most gorgeous guys. so as this moment im goign to purdue (assuming i dont fall in love wiht iowa and dont get accept to U of I.) it could be totally awesome though. me and laura(who also is going topurdue) are gonna room together we are both 96.9% we are going! (haha right laura?!!?) it would be a blast.  today in pysch we got yelled at like 2394783475 times becayse we were talking abotu it.  we are officialy freaks we already made diagrams of where all our furniture will go and stuff and who will bring what!  thinking about that made me happy! this just reinstates my bipolar theory. OY
Leave me love - i could use it right now

I know i havent exactly updated in awhile, but i swear im gonna make an effort to update more regularly.  I dont even know why im just in a really good mood. Life is awesome right now for absolutely no reason! I think this is the best kidn of happiness, when you are just happy for no reason.  Schools been okay. friends have been awesome - love you girls. parents have been shakey. but life is good.  Tonight OC premire! HELL YEA! and parents anniversary so fam dinner. Tomorrow is the weekend. HURRAY! Boys soccer made it to state. GOOD LUCK SPARTANS TOMORROW! ALl the other fall sports are doing amazing! GO GBN! Senior year is more then 1/4 over - freaky and i finally get to visit colleges this weekend. YAY!  Ill post when i get back and tell everyone all about my visits! Mwah for now!

Do you ever get that feeling that nothing is goinng your way? This is ridiculous i used to be a such a happy person and life was awesome. what is wrong with me?!  For once, i just want something to work out the way i planed. Nothing else to report leave some love.

Amanda yelled at me for not updating, so this entry is dedicated to her. : )  Too bad i dont really have anything exciting to share.  I guess ill write about my weekend.  Friday was really fun even though we didnt do much.  I honestly could've cared less about what we did just as logn as i was out.  We went out to dinner and saw a movie with this guy amanda works with. Then saturday night was a blast. We celbrated Amandas birthday with her and her fam and rented a wacked out movie. (im not even gonna go into details about that one) Im too tired to tired anymore, ill add more later maybe.

Wow, its been a few weeks since my last entry. Nothing too major has happened. I went to barcelona, Spain. Which was amazing until i got either food poisoning or the flu.  My parents had firts class and my brother and i had coach so on the way back my mom felt sorry for me and switched seats. so that was definatly a plus. It was cool; the chairs turned into a bed! anyways, now back to reality. A part of me wished i didnt miss this much school.  Im like failing all my classes. OKay so im nto really failing but it seems that way to me. ill admit it im an over achiever and the grades im getting are jsut not the grades im happy wiht and its really upsetting me. i guess it will be okay its still is only first quarter so all i have to do is work my ass off the next couple of weeks to raise them back up. OY! its stressin me out just thinking about it.  The joke is i always told myself that senior i wouldnt care about grades cuz ill all ready be accepted into college, but somehow i still want to succede. oh well. On the college subject, i have heard from 5 of the 7 schoosl i applied to. and ive gotten into all of them. (Purdue, univ. of indiana, univ. of iowan, ISU, and Drake) but 1/2 of those were my safetys and i still need to hear from University of Illinois and Wisconisn. So who knows. and no i havent visited any of them yet. this too is causing major issues. My parents, for some wacked out reason, wouldnt let me visit schools unitl i got accepted, but now im accepted they want me to visit during the week to "get a true sense of the campous". THIS IS BULLSHIT! i cant miss anymore school. i will fail out for real if i do. all i know is when my kids are going through this whole process, im going about it way differently.  OKay well i gotta go plan all these college visits.

So i officially have senoritis (no clue how to even spell that) i just cant wait to get out of here and have a chance to start over. at the same time it is really sad realizing that on friday I had my last loyality day assembely and odds are i am NEVER gonna see half of these people ever again. oh well, thats life.  On a happier note, there is a very good possibility that school will be cancelled tomo for Northbrook. I guess something wiht the water broke and they had to shut it off but after they turn it back on you have to boil water for 2 days. so my quesiton is how is the cafeteria gonna make lunch? isnt it a law that the schools have to seve lunch? i doubt they will boil their water before they use it? Hmmm...i guess we'll find out tomorrow. Last night sucked i felt sorta shitty all day but NEEDDED TO GO OUT, well come like 630ish as im starting to ger ready i start to feel really weird, sorta like im gonna pass out. anywways as it turns out my momma thinks i was dehydrated so i rested a bunch last night and feel all better. i guess it wasnt soo bad i got a chance to do some thinking and figured out who was incredibally fake, and who is a genunine friend....I thank those of you who cared abotu me and told me they hoped i felt better, that worked made me feel a lot better : )
otay, well its time to finish this homework. Yuck. Leave some love, it makes me happy (but then again i doubt you really really care about that)!

YES! College applications are finished and i can have a life again! After much crying, fighting with parents, crying again, then fighting somemore they are completeed and being mailed out tomorrow. WHAT A RELIEF!! Everyone says senior year is soo amazing...its been hell so far - way to much strss. but hopefully that will all turn around I decided to apply to [no particular order]
1. University of Wisconsin
2. University of Illinois
3. Indiana Universioty
4. University of Iowa
5. Purdue
6. Drake 
7. Illinois State
I still might apply to U ofkansas, U of minnesota, and some others but not right now.
Hopefully I can at least get into one of them...anyways, 
I miss being able to go out lol! But next weekend we be amazing!! Megan and amanda, you best not be at bradley the whole weekend : ) The part that will suck is now that im done, all my friends are goign to be starting this hell process so who knows how that will play out. oh well. Time to go study for my first math test this is not going to go well. my brain is soo fried but i didnt do too well on the quiz... and we dont want a repeat. 
Peace out much love to all!

Yes, to all of you out there who said I wouldnt have the balls to quite the daycare...I DID IT! the director was a complete dick and gave me so much crap for it but i dont have to go there everagain so thats great! Today went really well. It was late arrival so i got to sleep and i didnt really have any classes today.  Im soo excited, im in child dev. seminar and i get to leave school in the middle of the day to  be a teachers asistent at meadowbrook. I havent been there in like 6 years. it should be really fun.  Tomorrow is a B day, yuck, all my academics. But my physics teacher is blind and she is training a seeing eye dog. so we have a golden lab puppy in the class. ABSOLUTLEY ADORABLE! its the only thing keeping me from dropping that class. More to come later, peace for now

Wow, i cant even remember the last time i updated. I guess i have been sorta preocupied.  First my parents are INSANE about all this college shit...they wont even let me out of the house until its all done, thats not normal!!  The good news is that im basically done with all the applications and personal statement stuff - whew, what a relief. 
       On a totally other subject, stuff right now is really messed up and im not exactly sure when or how everything got this way.  All i know is i can not wait for it to go back to normal...i hope it does : / 
      I know i havent been the best friend recently i have just been going through a really weird time, i cant even describ it and i appologize for that.  I think everything is okay between me and everyone, but im not 100% sure.  I miss the way the fab 7 was.  I feel like my life is serioiusly falling apart right now and it sucks! Megan had an away message that freaked me out a bit because it puts into words all my feelings...

"do you ever just get that feeling where you dont want to talk to anybody? you dont wanna smile and you dont wanna fake being happy, but at the same time you dont know exactly what is wrong either. there isnt a way to explain it to someone who doesnt already understand. if you could want anything in the world it would be to be alone. people have stopped being comforting and being alone never was. at least when youre alone no one will constantly ask you whats wrong and there isnt anyone who wont take 'i dont know' for an answer. you feel the way you do just because. you hope the feeling will pass soon so youll be able to be yourself again. but until then, all you can do is wait..."

After reading that it got me to relieze a few things.  I guess I needed some time to just think i dont really know, but im ready to TURN MY LIFE AROUND! no more of this self pitty crap. I took for granted how absolutlely amazing my friends are and Im sorry 1853975 times!  you guys are all terrific, and i know i havent shown it recently but i really appriciate it.  THis is our last year together, I want to make it unforgetable before we all go our seperate ways.  So hopefully we can all put behind us the things that were said...or left unsaid and just look forward to a fabulous senior year. My BFFs (and you each know who you are) you mean so much to me and Im gonna try my hardest to make things alright again...

Today went fairly well.  Camp actually went by quickly. It was madri gras day and I definatly made 29735943 necklaces (okay so im exagerating a bit) anyone want one? they are super pretty! 
Then i had to work at the day care. YUCK! even though i only work once a week, it is way too much.  
Nothing really eventful happened today, but it was still a good day. 
Tomorrow is NB park district swim night...should be interesting. Hopefully it will get rained out cuz i just dont really want to go.  haev i mentioned how sick I am of camp? CUZ I AM! i dont liek children anymore or half of the staff...okay so i lied there are only liek 2 counselors that dont annoy me and one of them is the director. its just not a good situation.

Does anyone know how to make one of those cool lj? Mine is way to boring i want a pretty one!

Im glad to report that things are slowly but surely getting back to normal...no i take that back, better then normal. : )  Friday night was a blast. megans parents went out of town and enough said. Todays is my mommas birtday so im not allowed to go out.  The one night I actually feel like getting all ready and stuff im not allowed to - just great.  Thats okay i guess there is always tomorrow. Speaking of tomorrow, it starts the last week of camp for the year! YES! im sooo sick of it. I cant deal with small children anymore.   Then one week from tonday its cruise time! Hell yaz! im soo excited for that. I need to get tan. this summer has diffinatly had a lack of sun. YUCK. 
On a totally different subject, Im quitting my job at the day care. HURRAY! once again for the same reasons, IM SICK OF WATCHING KIDS! Any suggestions of how to quite? I need to find a new job though. I applied to work at the front desk of the Glenview Park District. Its where Haley works and would be so great to work with her, but they havent called me yet. So keep your fingers crossed it seems like a cool job.

I hate to use the cliche quote but i think i might have opened a bag of worms.  Everyone always tells me to share how Im feeling or whatever.  I know that each of my friends has told me when Im pissed about something that i shouldnt keep it all inside - like i usually do...so i took their advise and shared everything on my mind.  Maybe i shouldnt have i dont really know. I want all my friends to know that you mean the world to me and im not trying to upset any of you, i just needed to get this off my back. i completely agree that "they probably dont realize that it affects you in the way that it has" but it does.  you guys are  really great best friends, but recently i have just felt like crap and this seemed llike the best way to tell everyone whats been on my mind recently. its a whole lot easier to type what im thinking than to talk in person or whatever.  so hopefully i got whatever i needed to out in the open and things will start to look up. I HONESTLY LOVE ALL OF YOU VERY MUCH but those little things sometimes add up and then one tiny event pushes you over the edge and thats what basically happened. Megan had a really good quote today on her away message "everytime you go through a tough time you feel like dying but you need to accept the fact that its how life goes. life is about pain, happiness, sadness, love and excitement."  I guess i need to remeber that quote and remind myself that without the hard times you would never be able to appriciate all the great times.  
PS it would be great if you could at least stand behind the comments you are making and sign your names! : )

I know I had a live journal a few months ago, but i decided to delete it...well its back.  I need a way to vent - and this is a perfect way.  I really dont even know who I can turn to anymore to just talk, so this is bascially my only option.  I cant go crying to my mom, she will think im going pysco. and for my friends, well i sometimes dont think they realize i even exsist.   I know that sounds really harsh; but thats exactly the way i feel right about now. and im sick of it.  When I do actually go out I come home and end up crying. So its gotten to the point where its easier to just not go out.  I cant take it anymore and i honestly dont know what to do. you know how in groups of friends there is always that one person who noone really likes, she is the one who always strays behind them when walking,nobody realluy wants to sit in the front when she drives  and noone really notices or cares  about her- Well thats me. For once i  want to be that girl who is in the center of the group, not following in the shadow.  This is gonna sound really stupid but it reall bothers me why is that when we are hanging out my  arm is never grabed to come along when we are going somewhere.  For those of you who have no clue what im even talking about (and odds are that is most of you seeing that Im just rambling on and on) My friends do this thing were they grab each others arms when they go places, really cute, right? Except my arm is never the one grabbed. i know this sounds really petty but it hurts. What, are you ashamed of me? am i not good enough or pretty enough for you to be associated with me? I sometimes wonder why they are even friends with me? I truthfully question if they actually like me? Whenever I am with them I feel like im the reject of the group. You know, the one noone really likes but everyone just sorta feels sorry for them.  I dont know if its my own insecurities or what but sometimes i think the entire world hates me and my  "best friends" dont make that feeling any better.  I know that all of my friends are going to be really hurt by this update but im sorry I cant keep it inside anymore. Everything in my life is falling apart right now, and when I needed my friends the most it seems like they could care less. Im fed up with everyone being so damn self centered! reality check - there are othger people in this world than yourself!  Im not writting this to get pitty from anyone or put anyone on a guilt trip and im really sorry if that comes off this way. My purpose in writting this is to prevent my head from exploding from all these emotions.   I feel that im a fairly nice person and that gets taken advantage of way too many times. wow, that felt good now that im done being a bitch i want you to know this is not going out to all my friends. i ahve 2 or 3 girls that are truely good people and have been there for me and I thank you 184975 times for that. I dont even know anymore, maybe im beeing oversensative...or maybe not sensative enough...all I know is i feel like crap and my getting all my feelings out in the open like this has helped a whole lot.
